high_descs: Go across to the sofa.
Pick up the watermelon slice on the sofa closer to the pillow.
Turn right and go around to the front of the side table.
Place the watermelon on the side table near the left side.
Head back to the sofa.
Pick up the watermelon slice from the right side of the sofa.
Turn around and go back to the front of the side table.
Place the watermelon slice on the side table behind the other watermelon.
anns.task_desc: Place two slices of watermelon on the side table in front of the sofa.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the sofa.
Pick up water melon from the sofa.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the side table.
Place water melon on the side table.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sofa.
Pick up water melon from the sofa.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the side table.
Place water melon on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Collecting water melon from different places and arranging them on a side table.

high_descs: Walk towards and turn right to the sofa.
Pick the fruit from the sofa.
Turn right and turn right to the side table.
Place the fruit on the side table.
Turn left to the sofa.
Pick the fruit from the sofa.
Turn right and turn right to the side table.
Place the fruit on the side table.
anns.task_desc: To place the fruit on the side table.
